OL,5, A mother whose son was killed by an    
OL,6, unlicensed driver filmed drinking cider
OL,7, at the wheel has urged people to report
OL,8, illegal drivers.                       
OL,10,FDafydd Hughes, 18, died after his drunk
OL,11,Ffriend, who had also been taking drugs,
OL,12,Fcrashed his Ford Focus head-on while   
OL,13,Fspeeding on the wrong side of the road.
OL,15,FDafydd's mum said she could not forgive
OL,16,FRicky Davies, who was for jailed for   
OL,17,Feight years.                           
OL,19,F"I'm still numb," Emma Hughes told BBC 
OL,20,FWales' Crash Detectives programme.     
